item.title: CVE-2017-0357|2024-08-05T13:03:56.485Z -- iucode-tool -- iucode-tool
item.description: A heap-overflow flaw exists in the -tr loader of iucode-tool starting with v1.4 and before v2.1.1, potentially leading to SIGSEGV, or heap corruption.
